description: Commands to manage artifacts in a artifact store.

commands.name: az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact list
commands.summary: List all the available artifacts in the parent Artifact Store.
commands.syntax:
az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact list --artifact-store-name
                                               --publisher-name
                                               --resource-group
                                               [--max-items]
                                               [--next-token]
examples: az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact list --resource-group contoso-aosm --publisher-name contoso --artifact-store-name contoso
